{"tid":1177028,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"一早話左勝利OPPA係無辜 勝利夜店「Burning Sun」改名重新開張","createTime":"2019-05-29T14:29:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T16:36:59.000Z","uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"40322b882f2e2d105448cf5ed104a0b6f3be03cd","tid":1177028,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T14:29:27.000Z","msg":"南韓歌手勝利（本名李昇炫，이승현）在1月爆出他所投資的夜店Burning Sun疑似酒後撿屍女客，之後接連扯出背後一堆黑幕，勝利退出演藝圈止血但同時皆否認犯罪，直到本月18日出現才承認有過性交易。不過夜店Burning Sun在停業兩個月後，爆出近來悄悄重新開張。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3977/d3977431.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3977%2Fd3977431.jpg&h=b28d6332&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲勝利投資的夜店「Burning Sun」，造成南韓演藝圈大地震。（圖／CFP）<br />\n<br />\n南韓新聞節目MBC《Straight》報導，先前爆出性招待、吸毒等醜聞而結束營業的「Burning Sun」，近來悄悄改名為「Label」重新開張，且延續先前的VIP經營模式，依舊聚集許多男男女女徹夜狂歡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4129/d4129836.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4129%2Fd4129836.jpg&h=1a548d79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「Burning Sun」重新開張，並寫下「KING IS BACK」。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／탐사기획스트레이트）<br />\n<br />\n荒謬的是，他們不但打上「KING IS BACK」（王者回歸）的標語囂張嗆聲，更赫然將先前踢爆該夜店醜聞的《想知道真相》片段放在大螢幕上，似乎想表達對於先前事件不以為然。節目播出後再次引爆軒然大波，讓網友驚訝說道：「這下我相信韓劇演的都是真的了！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4129/d4129835.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4129%2Fd4129835.jpg&h=94db8a9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「Burning Sun」重新開幕，甚至將《想知道真相》片段放上螢幕。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／탐사기획스트레이트）<br />\n<br />\n勝利自2月底起共接受18次調查，對於涉嫌包含性買賣、仲介性買賣、貪汙夜店公款、違反食品衛生法共4項罪名始終否認有罪。而警方雖已確認勝利在自宅有性交易的行為，但勝利表示，「承認有發生性關係，但不是性交易。」14日在法院以沒有確切的證據、難以舉證為由正式駁回羈押聲請。不過勝利在18日承認性交易，坦言先前礙於藝人身分才不承認。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acbae81698a899ec5587eed176061a7617cbdda5","tid":1177028,"uid":256122,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T14:29:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e1f73e118d6feac0e37fa338d0b56cc62d7b4ce","tid":1177028,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T14:30:11.000Z","msg":"勝利巴又要改名"},{"pid":"3cf5d019aae4eb88b1ceb01df1a234f70fc41198","tid":1177028,"uid":256122,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T14:30:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4a2c26a326b82d5ff3980237841eb4025cfcc42","tid":1177028,"uid":74065,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T14:30:24.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 邊伯賢良淑德2<br />\n<br />\n唔記得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b2a8fef1e4f54ad77e2f8a1fd843904cbfb89f1","tid":1177028,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T14:30:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9f76841f3c067bd0fc48a0e8acc8e0a72eb1d51","tid":1177028,"uid":254461,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T14:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/1621751_10151928658331524_403459612_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2F1621751_10151928658331524_403459612_n.jpg&h=dd26aeb4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"349cc1c96f8805d7e115d949ec6ceff849140bdf","tid":1177028,"uid":256122,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T14:30:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02dd5253c3975543713e786d38928f9e2aa163f4","tid":1177028,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T14:30:59.000Z","msg":"見證牙邊新ac洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cla